.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://www.clevelandneurocare.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/Paediatric-EEG1-300x200.jpg 300w, http://www.clevelandneurocare.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/Paediatric-EEG1-768x512.jpg 768w, http://www.clevelandneurocare.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/Paediatric-EEG1-1024x683.jpg 1024w, http://www.clevelandneurocare.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/Paediatric-EEG1.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>\n			</dt></dl>\n			<br style=\'clear: both\' />', 'EEG', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'eeg', '', '', '2019-06-01 18:42:28', '2019-06-01 18:42:28', '', 0, 'http://www.clevelandneurocare.com/?page_id=14', 0, 'page', '', 0),
