				EEG Paediatric\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										EEG Routine\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										EEG Video\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										EEG Bed side\n									</li>\n						</ul>\n					<ul>\n							<li >\n										Nerve conduction studies (NCSs) \n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Diabetic neuropathy \n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Peripheral Neorupathy\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Myasthenia Gravis\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Facial nerve palsy\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										GuillainBarr syndrome\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Radiculopathy \n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Sciatic nerve injury\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Radial nerve palsy\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Ulnar nerve palsy or ulnar neuropathy.\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Femoral Nerve\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Plantar Nerve\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Carpal tunnel syndrome or median nerve\n									</li>\n						</ul>\n					<ul>\n							<li >\n										Needle electromyography (EMG)\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Myopathy\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Motor neuron diseases (MND)\n									</li>\n						</ul>\n					<ul>\n							<li >\n										Evoked potentials\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Somato sensory evoked potential study (SSEP)\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Brain stem auditory evoked potential (BAER)\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Visual Evoked potential (VEP)\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Sympathetic skin response\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Blink reflex or Corneal reflex\n									</li>\n						</ul>', 'Neurology', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '10-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-09-23 01:20:01', '2020-09-23 01:20:01', '', 10, 'http://www.clevelandneurocare.com/?p=395', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
